{"tid":1977860,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"打飛機 揸波 色誘司機當車費","createTime":"2020-04-18T09:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T11:00:41.000Z","uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b87df3793a9ecb80683e3280c6d4675d29244a36","tid":1977860,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>打飛機 揸 波　色誘司機當車費</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U-T0Cpkqhh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU-T0Cpkqhh8&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppevZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=0f4de264\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U-T0Cpkqhh8</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞：兩名內地女子乘搭的士，疑為了優惠車資，竟願意替司機手淫及讓他摸胸。其中一女「坐言起行」，抓司機陽具，又自掀襯衫，坦露乳房。司機坐懷不亂，嚴詞拒色誘陷阱。司機叫兩女落車後才發現手提電話不知所終，在附近街頭截獲一人，她曾交出 2,000 多元要求司機放過她。<br />\n記者：戴國輝"},{"pid":"c550d7164049c8f4319fe69d6c83ac79ef9e4cb3","tid":1977860,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/235135_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F235135_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4863f5ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/235203_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F235203_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a48e0c97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/235300_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F235300_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=00d44dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservi